    <item>
      <title>交易员撤离引发巨幅波动，可可价格暴跌创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cocoa-slumps-26-in-two-days-paring-back-historic-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可豆价格跌幅创历史新高——短短两天内暴跌27%——由于有能力维持交易头寸的投资者和公司越来越少，价格波动变得更加极端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cocoa-slumps-26-in-two-days-paring-back-historic-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 09:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国领导人暗示将出台新计划来解决经济面临的最大拖累</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-s-top-leaders-will-study-steps-to-digest-housing-stockpile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国执政的共产党誓言要探索新措施来解决旷日持久的住房危机（该危机仍然是中国经济的最大拖累），并暗示未来可能会降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-s-top-leaders-will-study-steps-to-digest-housing-stockpile</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
